ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisAuthority to enter into an individual AGREEMENT RESPECTING BIOLOGY CASEWORK ANALYSIS with each of seven provinces and one with the territory of YUKON which provides for the sharing of costs associated with the forensic analysis of biological evidence arising out of criminal investigations.
